data.description: *Price Adjustment-Motivated Sellers*Welcome to Arlen Oaks a family friendly neighborhood centrally located and within walking distance to local schools. This all-brick ranch style home with 2 car garage is situated on a large shady lot. As you enter, you'll be greeted by a bright spacious  open floor plan. The home has a split floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, laminate wood flooring, separate formal Living, Dining rooms and Family room with cozy fireplace. The Kitchen includes stainless steel appliances, ample cabinets, double pantry area, beautiful counter tops and Breakfast area. The owner's suite is very spacious, has trey ceiling, and two separate walk in closets. The ensuite bathroom has a separate shower/ garden tub (perfect for relaxing) , with double vanity sinks. Must see large backyard perfect for outdoor fun. This amazing home wont last long..Call for appointment today!
